results.title: To remove the sunset provision of section 203 of Public Law 105-384, and for other purposes.
results.short_title: To remove the sunset provision of section 203 of Public Law 105-384, and for other purposes.
results.summary: (This measure has not been amended since it was introduced. The expanded summary of the House passed version is repeated here.)  (Sec.1)This bill makes permanent the authority of Washington, Oregon, and California to adopt and enforce state laws governing fishing and processing in the exclusive economic zone adjacent to their state in any Dungeness crab fishery for which there is no fishery management plan in effect under the Magnuson-Stevens Fishery Conservation and Management Act.
